                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
                            <span>Kamerový systém non-stop</span>
